net.hudup.core.alg

Interface Aug

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Alg, AlgRemoteTask, AugRemoteTask, ExecutableAlg, ExecutableAlgRemoteTask, Exportable, Inspectable, ModelBasedAlg, ModelBasedAlgRemoteTask, NoteAlg, java.io.Serializable, SupportCacheAlg
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AugAbstract, AugRemoteWrapper

    public interface Aug
extends AugRemoteTask, ExecutableAlg, SupportCacheAlg, NoteAlg, Inspectable, java.io.Serializable
    This interface declares the most powerful algorithm and such algorithm is atomic. For example, some algorithms require recommendation results from recommendation algorithms. However, this interface is not categorized in AlgDesc2.MethodType. As a convention, any algorithm that implements this interface is called AUgorithm.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
